arStrings.szText: "Have you seen a boy named Chairul?"
That confused boy...I saw him leave with some men earlier. They were dressed like townspeople, but I saw the burns they were trying to hide.
I told Chairul not to speak to them, but he has been obsessed with strength and glory since his family died.
I'm worried. The Burned Knights are camped up by the old bridge while they repair it. Please, friend, will you look for him?
